data.description: Here is the perfect opportunity to put your finishing touches on a great home in a conveniently located north end neighborhood! Located in Kenlo Woods, this bi-level home has so much to offer. It is nestled on a double, corner lot and boasts nearly an acre. Inside you will find 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, a spacious kitchen and dining area, and two living spaces-one on each level. The large deck off of the kitchen is the perfect spot to entertain your family and friends. Call today for a showing!
